{
  "texts": [
    "We also offer a comprehensive overview of commonly employed solutions to these challenges.",
    "This adds practical value to those looking to adopt blockchain in real-world healthcare settings, particularly clinical trials.",
    "This makes the study theoretical and a practical resource that informs how blockchain solutions can be effectively deployed.",
    "Additionally, our review uniquely covers the evaluation of validation and verification processes and the specific metrics used during these implementations.",
    "The most significant difference of our study is that we designed a conceptual model based on the outcomes of this literature review, which, to the best of our knowledge, is the first in the literature to support both blockchain developers and healthcare researchers."
  ]
}